smartBore.description:
smartBore
If set to true, Iris will try to fill the insides of 'rooms' and 'pockets' where air should fit based off of raytrace checks. This prevents a village house placing in an area where a tree already exists, and instead replaces the parts of the tree where the interior of the structure is. 

This operation does not affect warmed-up generation speed however it does slow down loading objects.

Boolean
* Default Value is false
